title: Sports Clinic: The revolution of recovery methods at the hub of Sports Medicine
description: Aspetar recognizes the importance of effective recovery for athletes following their rigorous rehabilitation sessions. This episode highlights key recovery techniques, including sports massage, cold water immersion, and hot/cold contrast therapy.To ensure athletes maintain their fitness conditioning while recovering from injury, Aspetar provides a fully equipped recovery area, staffed by specialists trained to manage individual fitness needsThese steps not only protect the injured area but also enhance overall physical conditioning, ensuring a smooth transition back to sport.

description: Lens will face Monaco in Ligue 1 for the 108th time, the team that RCL have faced the most in the top-flight but also the one against which they have lost the most, with two defeats in the last three meetings. Lens are unbeaten in their last five matches to finish a Ligue 1 season, two of which came against Monaco. This is the third time in the last five years that the two teams have faced each other at Lens to close their season.

Since then, the 11 clashes between the two teams in the top-flight have seen eight wins for Paris and three for Auxerre.

title: Borussia Monchengladbach vs Holstein Kiel - Bundesliga 2024/25 Week 14
description: Borussia Monchengladbach and Holstein Kiel have met only twice before in professional football, with both meetings coming in the group stage of the Bundesliga promotion play-offs in June 1965. The Foals, as champions of the Regionalliga West, beat Regionalliga Nord table-toppers 1-0 in the first game. The Storks then won the return fixture 4-2 at home despite Gladbach twice going ahead through Jupp Heynckes and Gunter Netzer. Borussia Monchengladbach are unbeaten in their last seven Bundesliga games against promoted clubs. Gladbach have lost only once at home to a top-flight newcomer this century: 2-1 against RB Leipzig in February 2017.

title: Mainz 05 vs Bayern Munchen - Bundesliga 2024/25 Week 14
description: 1. FSV have also lost their last two competitive home games against the Munich side, most recently being beaten 4-0 in the second round of the DFB-Pokal in late October. 1. FSV Mainz 05 have won their last three Bundesliga home games against the side sitting top of the Bundesliga table, with all three wins coming against Bayern Munchen. Across the division, only Borussia Monchengladbach are currently on a longer winning run at home against league leaders.

title: Holstein Kiel vs Augsburg - Bundesliga 2024/25 Week 15

The two clubs have only previously faced off once in professional football: FCA won 1-0 in Kiel in the round of 16 of the DFB-Pokal in February 2019 thanks to Michael Gregoritsch’s goal. With five points from 14 games, Holstein Kiel are enduring the worst campaign by a Bundesliga debutant since Tasmania Berlin in 1965/66. No side has ever avoided relegation with a record as poor as Kiel’s right now.

title: Sports Clinic: The revolution of recovery methods at the hub of Sports Medicine
description: Aspetar recognizes the importance of effective recovery for athletes following their rigorous rehabilitation sessions. This episode highlights key recovery techniques, including sports massage, cold water immersion, and hot/cold contrast therapy.To ensure athletes maintain their fitness conditioning while recovering from injury, Aspetar provides a fully equipped recovery area, staffed by specialists trained to manage individual fitness needsThese steps not only protect the injured area but also enhance overall physical conditioning, ensuring a smooth transition back to sport.

title: Borussia Dortmund vs Bayer Leverkusen - Bundesliga 2024/25 Week 16
description: Bayer 04 Leverkusen have lost seven of their last nine Bundesliga away matches against Borussia Dortmund, the most away defeats of the Werkself against any team in the top flight since the start of the 2015-16 season. The two clubs drew 1-1 twice in the previous season - both times Leverkusen came back from a goal down. Since 2004, Borussia Dortmund has been unbeaten in both the first Bundesliga match of a new calendar year and in Friday home matches - both are ongoing records in BL history. In both cases, the last such defeat was a 0-1 at home to Schalke 04 in January 2004.

title: Freiburg vs Holstein Kiel - Bundesliga 2024/25 Week 16
description: SC Freiburg and Holstein Kiel have only met once in professional football - Kiel won 2-1 in the 2018-19 DFB-Pokal second round. Of the last five Bundesliga matches against promoted teams, Freiburg won only one, 1-0 at Darmstadt in April 2024. SCF also lost the last such encounter 0-3 at home to St. Pauli on matchday five at the end of September 2024. With 16 points from the first seven home games of this Bundesliga season, SC Freiburg got off to its shared best home start in the top flight. This means that SCF have already won as many home games this Bundesliga season as in the previous season.

title: Inside Sailing / 2025
description: Welcome to the 4th episode of Inside Sailing for 2025 - the TV program which brings you all the very best action from some of the most spectacular sailing events around the world. Through this epic sport we discover new horizons, new challenges, exciting journeys and some breathtaking sceneries.

title: World Sailing Show 2025
description: The World Sailing Show 2025 brings you the most thrilling moments from elite sailing competitions around the globe. From high-speed foiling action to tactical offshore battles, this episode covers top events like the America’s Cup, SailGP, and The Ocean Race. Meet the world’s best sailors, explore cutting-edge boat technology, and witness the drama of high-stakes racing on the water.

title: Nimes vs Montpellier - LNH Division 1 - French Handball Starligue
description: Dive into the excitement of French handball with Liqui Moly Starligue, formerly LNH Division 1. Established in 1952, this premier league event features 16 top teams battling for glory. With Montpellier’s 14 Handball titles and Paris Saint-Germains 11 wins, the competition is fierce. Champions earn spots in the EHF Champions League, while cup winners qualify for the European League.

title: PSG vs Istres - LNH Division 1 - French Handball Starligue
description: Paris Saint-Germain closes in on a historic 12th league title as they face Istres, a resilient side known for their fighting spirit. With key changes ahead on the bench and standout performances throughout the season, PSG looks to finish strong and begin a new chapter in their handball journey.

title: AR GKA Kite World Tour 2025
description: The Lords of Tram Big Air kiteboarding event is building reputation as one of the sports annual high points.A spectacular setting on the smooth lagoon waters of Parc des Dosses, at Barcarès, sits in the shadow of the snow-capped Pyrenees.

title: Al Rayyan vs Al Gharafa - Final Amir Cup 2025
description: Amir Cup is the biggest football cup competition in Qatar. It is an association football tournament played every season by all first and second division teams in Qatar.Al Sadd the most successful team who won the tournament are the defending champions.

title: Equestrian Global Tour Jumping Cannes 2025 - Round 1 – Team Competition
description: The world’s top riders and horses return to the French Riviera as the Longines Global Champions Tour stops in Cannes. Elite showjumping, speed, and precision under the lights in one of the tour’s most iconic coastal venues.
